{"tid":97520,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"到底大家飲酒為啲咩","createTime":"2017-01-27T16:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T15:51:29.000Z","uid":20736,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1607e3c6ce0f91d0337da9dc213444fff31437ad","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為醉<br />\n大家通常飲啲咩<br />\n飲開藍妹 唔識飲8度以上嘅酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f251c0a62b73bf5bf3dcb29c01aeceff142ae7b8","tid":97520,"uid":68953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"醉個種感覺<br />\n我都係飲藍妹多，時不時會飲下伏特加<br />\n利申，兩杯就訓低左"},{"pid":"aabd9cfdae47570061e1cae7d127d2dd16b30427","tid":97520,"uid":10030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"微醉 暈暈地唔係好行到直線 <br />\n知自己再飲就醉果時個feel好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5a0b9a031f5f7813cefa2a8431282c9b4adb8b","tid":97520,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"紅酒<br />\n<br />\n健康"},{"pid":"0c23751592e82a41a6f7d3d2a46a2b99e88c22e9","tid":97520,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"呃蝦條"},{"pid":"e245cc21ccfe6a4eceb098da8bce94f065938656","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg&h=53ef07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d686edae39a93ce9f5b7f5f3a78621015f8205","tid":97520,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:52:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg&h=53ef07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梅酒就加冰加梳打啦，一百蚊野雖然係粗少少，識飲都會好飲既"},{"pid":"e711ff4ecc7abdb317c5efa4f535ef40e2def683","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg&h=53ef07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梅酒就加冰加梳打啦，一百蚊野雖然係粗少少，識飲都會好飲既</blockquote><br />\n等我聽日買啲梳打<br />\n聽晚再試黎飲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有半支係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77b5d41b509790a12b70550ca11849fcbff631c","tid":97520,"uid":18708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg&h=53ef07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十幾分鐘隊兩支好難醉<br />\n通常飲啤酒求醉<br />\n我都係兩至三 啖飲晒成支大啤<br />\n五分鐘飲兩支就好快醉"},{"pid":"2f2127cd83c0759cb2680a3059ed7f11035531c8","tid":97520,"uid":79566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"想比個腦off 一晚就會飲到醉"},{"pid":"df63aff8d6272a7946c39ba1c5a3b1b7d26def5d","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0e1.jpg&h=53ef07fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十幾分鐘隊兩支好難醉<br />\n通常飲啤酒求醉<br />\n我都係兩至三 啖飲晒成支大啤<br />\n五分鐘飲兩支就好快醉</blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次飲嘅時候頭個幾啖都飲得好慢<br />\n覺得好難飲<br />\n通常飲左半支左右先會慣<br />\n先可以當水飲"},{"pid":"5b717ad52d3fd4136ce053796361043e2801ca54","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打唔鍾意一罐罐咁飲<br />\n淨鍾意用杯或者一樽樽咁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常用罐黎飲飲得好慢<br />\n用杯同樽飲就好快飲完一支"},{"pid":"d75a717bf01bf1f29542207fdd30315ad21e2593","tid":97520,"uid":70518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打唔鍾意一罐罐咁飲<br />\n淨鍾意用杯或者一樽樽咁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常用罐黎飲飲得好慢<br />\n用杯同樽飲就好快飲完一支</blockquote><br />\n罐飲氣量太多...會有少少那既感覺<br />\n樽裝都係<br />\n倒落杯會好飲好多"},{"pid":"e4d8f7a92bea2b28cd8334ff24e7c3c33cf798d8","tid":97520,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"為應酬，自己好憎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但天生體格真係飲唔醉唔知點解，老豆老母都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607c5552488d68420981b37caaa668555c3eb354","tid":97520,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"為開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545132cb8860530abae16e53b02cfb8d99e312ea","tid":97520,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"為左唔使吸毒咁進入hyper狀態"},{"pid":"22123374055e97cedcedad102a870ed759663b0c","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"有冇人飲過大眼仔 strobe<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84790b904c051a63ca40ac8d450538ee69afa968","tid":97520,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>微醉 暈暈地唔係好行到直線 <br />\n知自己再飲就醉果時個feel好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1247ad4a1a97fd11db7edb9f768345fec3e0dc30","tid":97520,"uid":66111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:43:03.000Z","msg":"求醉隊vodka啦<br />\n飲啤酒成肚氣又難醉<br />\nspecial brew另計"},{"pid":"c08a7da8d0e1ea7d2cca5c034a61721e93f9e917","tid":97520,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"要醉咪溝酒囉"},{"pid":"c842db519509dd84f5e231b7f7d916e7028e039c","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"想試飲vodka whiskey<br />\n但係咪一定要落吧先飲到<br />\n七仔個啲算唔算<br />\n七仔個啲最多都好似10幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3da9e6f32ffe00bafb2b3257e66a0d5ec411894","tid":97520,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"陪人飲<br />\n龍志力好強 逼自己醒<br />\n真係頂唔順就只會訓教唔發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f67190c73e4a10a6341b86e29b7e644e86ac37","tid":97520,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"頭先大家有冇上唔到連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4bf1a270f31ddf25eba32f3da389a9fb1fbb79","tid":97520,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>微醉 暈暈地唔係好行到直線 <br />\n知自己再飲就醉果時個feel好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b822544