/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日飲大咗，大家都喺當我鳩吹啦！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f063e66e608759c77aed93e04829972d0fec0b2","tid":97520,"uid":18708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0.jpg&h=a86f8779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十幾分鐘隊兩支好難醉<br />\n通常飲啤酒求醉<br />\n我都係兩至三 啖飲晒成支大啤<br />\n五分鐘飲兩支就好快醉</blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次飲嘅時候頭個幾啖都飲得好慢<br />\n覺得好難飲<br />\n通常飲左半支左右先會慣<br />\n先可以當水飲</blockquote><br />\n其實想慳返錢咋 都係求醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89409cf0c97aeccdc525549a287f87d310ba0f11","tid":97520,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲好多都唔醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過十幾分鐘隊晒兩支大啤藍妹都唔醉<br />\n淨係得少少high<br />\n依家試緊飲啲濃度高啲嘅酒<br />\n想快啲醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/28/004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F28%2F004859_9487c4092d7570f91db1a9418e71f0.jpg&h=a86f8779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日行百街見到100幾蚊 粗粗地買黎試下<br />\n雖然好甜 但都係有好多酒精味 好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十幾分鐘隊兩支好難醉<br />\n通常飲啤酒求醉<br />\n我都係兩至三 啖飲晒成支大啤<br />\n五分鐘飲兩支就好快醉</blockquote><br />\n高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次飲嘅時候頭個幾啖都飲得好慢<br />\n覺得好難飲<br />\n通常飲左半支左右先會慣<br />\n先可以當水飲</blockquote><br />\n其實想慳返錢咋 都係求醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀，開頭係難飲D,之後會越飲越純，係真架！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f89ec06d86b0ed03f38a65112c2681f2a52d56","tid":97520,"uid":18708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"最鍾意飲大枝裝 可以大口大口咁灌<br />\n同埋一個人飲酒 唔知點解會好易越飲越多<br />\n一罐接一罐"},{"pid":"22d85bd1eeb8587f6dc809d99968ae15d413624d","tid":97520,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最鍾意飲大枝裝 可以大口大口咁灌<br />\n同埋一個人飲酒 唔知點解會好易越飲越多<br />\n一罐接一罐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真喺！！<br />\n<br />\n我永遠一個人飲，唔知點解越飲越多，尋晚一個人飲咗八罐生力king can!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8150c14a6ff0f25722d9e5d0d32e86c5a3485992","tid":97520,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"享受味道<br />\n永遠唔會劈酒"},{"pid":"57439620e1e5971e27f47c58510b015271d469f7","tid":97520,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"飲完算唔算好訓啲？<br />\n<br />\n但起身會頭痛<br />\n<br />\n同埋半醉半醒半hyper個感覺好舒服<br />\n<br />\n好似放低左壓力咁"},{"pid":"f299c45d36a14486e85ccfeb73613ff1bf06d12c","tid":97520,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:33:38.000Z",